<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Kevin Zhu's favorite cookies</title>
        <style>
            .bg{
                background-image: url("https://lit.lhsmathcs.org/image/KevinZhu.jpeg");
                background-repeat: repeat;
                opacity: 0.3;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
                position: absolute;
                z-index: -1; 
                height: 300%; 
            }
            pre code {
                background-color: #eee;
                border: 1px solid #999;
                display: block;
                padding: 10px;
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            textarea {
            	width: 50%;
            	height: 400px;
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .whiteContainer {
                margin-top: 60px;
                margin-bottom: 60px;
                margin-left: 20%;
                background-color: white;
                box-shadow: 0 2px 3px rgba(8,8,8,0.1), 0 0 0 1px rgba(8,8,8,0.1);
                width: 60%;
                word-break: break-word;
                word-wrap: break-word;
                font-size: 18px;
                color: #404040;
                text-align: center;
            }
        </style> 
    </head>
    <body style="margin: 0;padding: 50px 50px 50px 50px;">
        <div class="bg"></div>
        <h1>Welcome to My (Kevin Zhu) Cookie üç™ shop!</h1>
        <div class="whiteContainer">
            <br>
        <% if (likeCookie === "false") { %>
            <p>I have so many cookies to share with you. Unfortunately, judging from your current cookies, it seems like you do not like any cookies üç™ :<. Thus I will not bother giving you any</p>
        <% } else if (likeCookie === "true") { %>
            <p>Oh silly you. What do you mean you like a true cookie? I have 20 cookies numbered from 1 to 20, and all of them are made from super true authentic recipes.</p>
        <% } else if (likeCookie === "17") { %>
            <p>Omg, I too love the 17th cookie. We must share a special connection ‚ù§Ô∏è! Just for you, I will add something special along with the cookie üç™, here <b><%= flag %></b>. Don't let the other customers know tho, they won't be happy.</p>
            <img src="https://cwatch.comodo.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/what-are-cookies.png" style="width: 100%">
        <% } else { %>
            <p>Hm okay. If you like the cookie number <%- likeCookie %> then here you go I guess. It's not my favorite cookie though</p>
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f1/2ChocolateChipCookies.jpg" style="width: 100%">
        <% } %>

            <br>
        </div>

    </body>
</html>
